Title: Throwaway
Plot: A planted gun in a truck-jacking case causes complications for the Strike Team, and now they're left to clean up their own mess. While the rift between Officers Lowe and Sofer deepens, causing Capt. Aceveda to intervene. Also, Detective Wyms deals with the mess of her family during a visit from her daughter.
GuestStars: Tangi Miller, Rolando Molina, K.K. Dodds, Roscoe Lee Browne, Mystro Clark
